{"tid":568143,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有沒有人覺得自己唔適合拍拖？","createTime":"2018-02-21T13:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T08:35:32.000Z","uid":53003,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"7a5e4d18e869f5be3bd69fa4606af8a8c1494bca","tid":568143,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T13:37:28.000Z","msg":"未拍之前會患得患失<br />\n拍咗之後都係咁，又發現自己有好強控制慾，雖然唔會真係控制佢或者同佢嘈，但佢有啲咩嘢唔符合自己想法的話，就會覺得唔舒服。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afcb40b90380d03091e897a07fe369a5c6cffcc4","tid":568143,"uid":154997,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7a5e4d18e869f5be3bd69fa4606af8a8c1494bca","tid":568143,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T13:37:28.000Z","msg":"未拍之前會患得患失<br />\n拍咗之後都係咁，又發現自己有好強控制慾，雖然唔會真係控制佢或者同佢嘈，但佢有啲咩嘢唔符合自己想法的話，就會覺得唔舒服。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T13:48:21.000Z","msg":"比人背叛過<br />\n暫時對愛情冇哂幻想<br />\n每逢夜晚/佳節倍感孤獨 <br />\n但好矛盾地對拍拖有恐懼<br />\n勸各位要識得保護自己 自私d<br />\n唔想再受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5008fc91dbea62e8beed15640b2a329ce0f763","tid":568143,"uid":170699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a5e4d18e869f5be3bd69fa4606af8a8c1494bca","tid":568143,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T13:37:28.000Z","msg":"未拍之前會患得患失<br />\n拍咗之後都係咁，又發現自己有好強控制慾，雖然唔會真係控制佢或者同佢嘈，但佢有啲咩嘢唔符合自己想法的話，就會覺得唔舒服。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T13:50:28.000Z","msg":"冇安全感？"},{"pid":"574b9ecbcd514efc28f6086b0a46acd17ec74468","tid":568143,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T13:50:44.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"e2fc1953f6a1b35fcb84e7670133df7cdadda515","tid":568143,"uid":3775,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T13:50:56.000Z","msg":"我<br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己一個人先最好 唔會