/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會好唔舒服，覺得自己鍾意佢多過佢鍾意自己，正如有一日我唔搵佢佢又真喺唔搵我，就會開始好負面"},{"pid":"769213229e502165558e690e912849861ee7e269","tid":568143,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afcb40b90380d03091e897a07fe369a5c6cffcc4","tid":568143,"uid":154997,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7a5e4d18e869f5be3bd69fa4606af8a8c1494bca","tid":568143,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T13:37:28.000Z","msg":"未拍之前會患得患失<br />\n拍咗之後都係咁，又發現自己有好強控制慾，雖然唔會真係控制佢或者同佢嘈，但佢有啲咩嘢唔符合自己想法的話，就會覺得唔舒服。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T13:48:21.000Z","msg":"比人背叛過<br />\n暫時對愛情冇哂幻想<br />\n每逢夜晚/佳節倍感孤獨 <br />\n但好矛盾地對拍拖有恐懼<br />\n勸各位要識得保護自己 自私d<br />\n唔想再受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T14:43:36.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;或許我的心包有一層硬殼，能破殼而入的東西是極其有限的。所以我才不能對人一往情深。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n而家我覺得因為太過保護自己而錯過左太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慢慢黎，慢慢開放自己俾一個修補內傷既人吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a875dd262a2f28f0eceee123078557d4dc53de50","tid":568143,"uid":15011,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T14:50:00.000Z","msg":"覺。自己較多負能量，好驚拍咗拖會不斷放負，搞到大家都辛苦。同埋好驚如果對一個人有期望，就會有更大嘅失望同背叛。"},{"pid":"bc14b111c9bff1e205cc3ce0158fe1cabc555046","tid":568143,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:05:09.000Z","msg":"唔拍拖點做愛<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/230453_768d7698401e10bc845aa853af04b2a6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F230453_768d7698401e10bc845aa853af04b2a6.gif&h=680cc3a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/230453_768d7698401e10bc845aa853af04b2a6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi